    - "Requirements alignment is rated HIGH with citations to requirements/project.md, requirements/pipeline.md, and requirements/observability.md. The ticket body itself does not reference any of them. The quoted fragments are generic enough that almost any state-file ticket would 'align'. 'No conflicts detected' is asserted, not demonstrated."
    - "Requirements alignment cites bin/overnight-status as 'direct in-repo prior art'. Prior art is not a requirement. A precedent binary existing is not the same as a requirements document mandating this pattern."
